Enter productions (use # for epsilon):
Production 1: E=E+T
Production 2: E=T

Grammar after removing LEFT RECURSION:
E=TE'
E'=+TE' | #

FIRST Sets:
FIRST(E) = { T }
FIRST(Z) = { + # }

FOLLOW Sets:
